               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction
 - Letter of Eusebius to Carpanius (fols.
                     1va-1vb)
 - Canon Tables (fols. 2r-5r)
 II) Gospel of Matthew (fols.
                     5va-43vb)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 68 titles
                     (fols.5va-6ra)
 - Bǝsrāta Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 7ra-43va)
                     - Postscript (fol. 43vb)
 III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 44ra-65va)
 - List
                     of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Mark: 48 titles (fols.44ra-44rb)
 -
                     Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols. 45ra-65va)
 - Postscript (fol.
                     65va)
 IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 65va-103va)
 - List of the “tituli”
                     for the Gospel of Luke: 83 titles (fols. 65va-66rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās
                     “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 67ra-103va)
 - Postscript (fol. 103va)
 V)
                     Gospel of John (fols. 103vb-137va)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel
                     of John: 19 titles (fol. 103vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols.
                     105ra-137rb)
 - Postscript (fols. 137rb-137va)
 - Postscript for the
                     four Gospels (fol. 137va)
 
 Additiones 1-10; colophon.</summary>
